      <title><![CDATA[Markdown实践笔记]]></title>
      <url>http://bito.cc/markdown-note/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="关于Markdown解析引擎的怪异行为记录"><a href="#关于Markdown解析引擎的怪异行为记录" class="headerlink" title="关于Markdown解析引擎的怪异行为记录"></a>关于Markdown解析引擎的怪异行为记录</h2><p><em>（注：此处只使用Github、Gitlab、Marked解析引擎进行实践）</em></p>
<h3 id="1-关于列表与代码块"><a href="#1-关于列表与代码块" class="headerlink" title="1. 关于列表与代码块"></a>1. 关于列表与代码块</h3><p><strong>如果列表中嵌入代码块，则列表元素之前必须空一行，否则Github、Gitlab不能正常识别代码块。</strong><br>例子：<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>item 1</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>item 2</div><div class="line">  <span class="code">```css</span></div><div class="line">  @charset 'utf-8';</div><div class="line">  body &#123;</div><div class="line">    font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';</div><div class="line">    font-size: 16px;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">  ```(此括号注释，请手动删除)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Github处解析出来的结果为：<br><a id="more"></a><br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-github-error.png" alt=""><br>Gitlab中的表现同样异常，见下图：<br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-gitlab-error.png" alt=""><br>在列表元素之间加入空行，markdown代码改为：<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>item 1</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>item 2</div><div class="line">  <span class="code">```css</span></div><div class="line">  @charset 'utf-8';</div><div class="line">  body &#123;</div><div class="line">    font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';</div><div class="line">    font-size: 16px;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">  ```(此括号注释，请手动删除)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>此时，Github以及Gitlab结果都正常了，见下图：<br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-github-right.png" alt=""><br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-gitlab-right.png" alt=""><br>Github、Gitlab都需要要加空行，而Marked解析引擎则加不加空行都是正常的。<em>（什么？上图的代码缩进不正常了？见下文的“<a href="#2-关于缩进与代码块">关于缩进与代码块</a>”）</em></p>
<h3 id="2-关于缩进与代码块"><a href="#2-关于缩进与代码块" class="headerlink" title="2. 关于缩进与代码块"></a>2. 关于缩进与代码块</h3><p><strong>缩进必须是四个空格，否则缩进后的代码块在Gitlab中解析缩进不正常</strong>。<br><em>（注：如果直接在Github或Gitlab平台中直接编辑markdown文档就会发现，两个平台按一次Tab键默认缩进的字符数是不一样的，Github默认缩进两个字符，Gitlab默认缩进四个字符）</em><br>例子：<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>item 1</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>item 2</div><div class="line">  <span class="code">```css</span></div><div class="line">  @charset 'utf-8';</div><div class="line">  body &#123;</div><div class="line">    font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';</div><div class="line">    font-size: 16px;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">  ```(此括号注释，请手动删除)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>Gitlab处解析出来的结果为：<br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-gitlab-right.png" alt=""><br>代码缩进不正常了，第三、四行前面少了两个空格。<br>Github中的表现则是正常的：<br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-github-right.png" alt=""><br>将markdown的缩进改为四个空格，如下：<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>item 1</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>item 2</div><div class="line"><span class="code">    ```css</span></div><div class="line"><span class="code">    @charset 'utf-8';</span></div><div class="line"><span class="code">    body &#123;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="code">      font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';</span></div><div class="line"><span class="code">      font-size: 16px;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="code">    &#125;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="code">    ```(此括号注释，请手动删除)</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>此时，Github以及Gitlab结果都正常了，见下图：<br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-github-right.png" alt=""><br><img src="/markdown-note/eg-gitlab-indent.png" alt=""><br>Gitlab需要四个空格缩进，而Github、Marked则不论两个字符还是四个字符的缩进都解析正常。</p>
